<lb n="0516b13" ed="X"/><lb n="0158b16" ed="R016"/><cb:juan n="1" fun="close"><cb:jhead>大方廣圓覺脩多羅了義經近釋卷一</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>